Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:57.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}その頂きへと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}I'm proud of myself and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:05.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}We must be the change we wish to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:05.26,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}在囚籠中是絕對安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:10.44,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}但忘卻了創造的地方不會有光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.93,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}訴說希望 驅散不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.82,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}革命的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:19.38,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}突破到無人能及的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:25.33,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}總有一天要超越修羅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:30.92,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}就算現在壓倒性的支配讓我極度乾渴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:35.43,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}只有夢不會被奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}燃燒吧 全部神經的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:43.12,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}不知誰能收到的聲音裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:48.45,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}不會有意義
